dam.name: Roxie
dam.description: Roxie is a nurturing and calm mother, always attentive to her pups. She has a gentle nature that brings comfort and warmth to everyone around her.

sire.name: Clifford
sire.description: Clifford is a proud and loving father, known for his intelligence and gentle demeanor. He has a joyful presence that lights up the room.

dam.name: Daisy
dam.description: Daisy is cheerful and playful, always bringing energy and warmth wherever she goes. Her friendly demeanor makes her a joy to be around.

sire.name: Damion
sire.description: A gentle giant! Damion is calm and composed, known for his gentle and steady presence. He has a quiet confidence that puts everyone at ease.

dam.name: Beauty
dam.description: Beauty always exudes grace and serenity. She has a nurturing spirit that brings peace and joy to everyone she encounters. Whether it's caring for her pups or simply being by your side, Beauty's gentle presence is a constant source of comfort and love

sire.name: Luke
sire.description: Luke is an AKC registered poodle with a great temperament and a happy demeanor, he is always happy to meet someone new. Luke thrives on being outside and getting lots of exercise.
